# Changelog

All notable changes to the Nigerian ANPR System will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [1.0.0] - 2026-02-20

###  Initial Release

#### Added
- **Core Detection Engine**
  - Real-time plate detection using OpenCV contour analysis
  - Multi-pass OCR with EasyOCR (3 threshold variants)
  - Nigerian plate format validation (AAA-000-AA)
  - Blur detection and frame stabilization
  - Cooldown protection to prevent duplicate logging
  
- **State Recognition System**
  - Direct OCR of state banner text
  - Fuzzy text matching for 36 Nigerian states
  - Auto-zoom feature for enhanced state detection
  - Smart caching (exact plate and prefix-based)
  - Automatic state backfilling across matching prefixes
  
- **Direction Tracking**
  - Alternating IN/OUT detection per vehicle
  - Persistent vehicle status (INSIDE/OUTSIDE)
  - Entry and exit counters
  
- **Database Layer**
  - SQLite storage with two tables (plate_detections, vehicle_tracking)
  - Persistent counters across restarts
  - State cache loading on startup
  
- **Web Dashboard**
  - Minimalistic black & white design
  - Live stats overview (Total, IN, OUT, Inside, Unique)
  - Quick analytics bar (Most Active State, Peak Hour, Avg/Hour)
  - Real-time detection feed (last 20 events)
  - State distribution bar chart (top 8 states)
  - Searchable vehicle registry table
  - Auto-refresh every 3 seconds
  
- **Vehicle Analytics Modal**
  - Total time inside (all-time cumulative)
  - Time inside today (current session)
  - Total visits counter
  - Current status with timestamp
  - Longest stay with date
  - Average stay duration
  - Recent activity timeline with durations
  
- **REST API**
  - `/api/stats` - Aggregate statistics
  - `/api/recent` - Last 20 detections
  - `/api/vehicles` - All tracked vehicles
  - `/api/today` - Hourly breakdown
  - `/api/states/today` - State distribution
  - `/api/vehicle/<plate>` - Vehicle analytics
  - `/api/search/<plate>` - Plate search
  - `/api/system/status` - System health
  
- **Configuration System**
  - Comprehensive config.py with 40+ tunable parameters
  - Detection thresholds (blur, stabilization, cooldown)
  - Plate geometry constraints (aspect ratio, area, size)
  - OCR settings (confidence threshold, auto-zoom)
  - Visual overlay colors
  - False positive filtering options
  
- **Launch System**
  - Unified launcher script (launcher.py)
  - Automatic browser opening
  - Threaded web server startup
  - Clean shutdown handling
  
- **Documentation**
  - Comprehensive README.md
  - Full technical documentation (Word format)
  - Contributing guidelines
  - Installation scripts (Windows batch file)
  - Requirements.txt with version pinning

#### Technical Details
- Python 3.9+ support
- YOLOv8 nano model for object detection
- EasyOCR 1.7+ for text recognition
- OpenCV 4.8+ for image processing
- Flask 3.0+ for web framework
- SQLite 3 for data persistence

